00:03:50,670 --> 00:03:52,170
<i>is dying or dead.</i>

91
00:03:52,172 --> 00:03:55,373
<i>We have no allies, we have no enemies...</i>

92
00:03:55,375 --> 00:03:59,711
<i>Just a world of sick, desperate people.</i>

93
00:03:59,713 --> 00:04:02,797
<i>If Dr. Scott has the makings of a cure,</i>

